OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain move
OL,6,Fsoutheast across central areas before
OL,7,Fclearing to the southeast later.
OL,8,FBrighter weather follows in the
OL,9,Fnorthwest with scattered showers, some
OL,10,Fheavy or wintry over northern hills.
OL,11,FWindy in the north and less cold than
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny lingering rain clears the
OL,15,Fsoutheast. Clear spells elsewhere with
OL,16,Fwintry showers. Later, persistent rain
OL,17,Fand hill snow reach Scotland, Northern
OL,18,FIreland and northern England. Windy,
OL,19,Fcolder, with frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
