OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSunny spells and showers,
OL,6,Fsome heavy and wintry with hail, hill
OL,7,Fsnow and isolated thunder. More
OL,8,Fprolonged showers for England and
OL,9,FWales later. Windy and blustery,
OL,10,Ffeeling colder than Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
